    <p>Carved-stone effect using multi-layer <code>text-shadow</code>. A light source from above creates a highlight on the upper edges and a deep shadow below, simulating script cut into warm sandstone. Unlike gradient effects, this uses <code>color</code> so <code>text-shadow</code> works natively.</p>
