          In Tibetan, "hello" is <span class="tr-jomolhari tr-guard tr-scale-up tr-baseline" lang="bo" style="color:#e2e8f0;">བཀྲ་ཤིས་བདེ་ལེགས།</span> — a common greeting.
        </p>
      </div>
