  <span class="tag">&lt;span</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="str">"tr-jomolhari tr-guard tr-scale-up <span class="hl">tr-baseline</span>"</span> <span class="attr">lang</span>=<span class="str">"bo"</span><span class="tag">&gt;</span>
    བཀྲ་ཤིས་བདེ་ལེགས།
  <span class="tag">&lt;/span&gt;</span> — a common greeting.
<span class="tag">&lt;/p&gt;</span></code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="doc-section" id="tr-shad-pair">
    <h3><code>.tr-shad-pair</code></h3>
    <p>Prevents double-shad (<span class="tr-jomolhari tr-guard" lang="bo" style="color:#e2e8f0;">། །</span>) from splitting across lines. Wrap the sequence in a <code>&lt;span&gt;</code>. Double-shad marks verse endings and must never be separated.</p>
