      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="doc-section" id="tr-nobr-tsheg">
    <h3><code>.tr-nobr-tsheg</code></h3>
    <p>Protects non-breaking tsheg + shad sequences (e.g. <span class="tr-jomolhari tr-guard" lang="bo" style="color:#e2e8f0;">ང་།</span>) from splitting. The tsheg before shad must never cause a line break. Also fixable via <code>terma.prepare()</code> which auto-replaces with non-breaking tsheg (U+0F0C).</p>
