  <section class="doc-section" id="tr-text-left">
    <h3>Text Alignment</h3>
    <p><code>.tr-text-left</code>, <code>.tr-text-center</code>, <code>.tr-text-right</code>, <code>.tr-text-justify</code> — standard alignment utilities.</p>
    <div class="code-standalone">
      <div class="code-block">
        <div class="code-block-header">
          <span class="code-block-title">HTML</span>
